name: User can delete any selected item from its three dots menu
description: Agile story : As a user, I should be able to upload a file, move or delete any selected file under the Files module
descriptionHtml: Agile story : As a user, I should be able to upload a file, move or delete any selected file under the Files module

testStage.description: Agile story : As a user, I should be able to upload a file, move or delete any selected file under the Files module

steps.name: Given  the user logs in with username "Employee10" and password "Employee123"
And  the user navigates to the File Module page
When  user clicks on three dots button near selected file-folder name "Boris"
And  user clicks on delete folder-file button, from option list provided
Then  user see selected folder-file name "Boris" is deleted
